def calculate_table_scores(N, first_row):
    list_n = list(range(1, N + 1))
    fin_list = []
    for k in range(N):
        list_n_flag = list_n[k:] - list_n[:k]
        res_list = [list_n_flag[i] + first_row[i] for i in range(N)]
        maxx = max(res_list)
        fin_list.append(maxx)
    return fin_list
